				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Qu%E1%BA%BF/Chinh-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-jXv3Mhp4R8lswL7DdYI7VA">Chinh đông ca kỳ 5 - 征東歌其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Qu%E1%BA%BF/author-XqKtUVvcrpGk9S-tbvHI0Q">Hàn Thượng Quế</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Anh/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Qu%E1%BA%A7n-ng%C6%B0-tri%E1%BB%81u-l%C3%BD-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-p_OnqEhO0wCOdBROF6KUrw">Đề “Quần ngư triều lý” đồ - 題群魚朝鯉圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Anh/author-lYMSgB5b1VLUWjgJGL6J2A">Chu Đường Anh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/H%E1%BB%AFu-c%C3%BA-v%C3%B4-c%C3%BA/poem-c2OkGpQkP4QQwP201dfBdQ">Hữu cú vô cú - 有句無句</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-EY7jN0xHQfiiJpD91KwIgw">Trần Nhân Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%AD-Ch%C3%A2n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/K%E1%BB%87-th%E1%BB%8B-ch%C3%BAng-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-J4J0xWXXt-fpGPi2hiq9BQ">Kệ thị chúng kỳ 3 - 偈示眾其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%AD-Ch%C3%A2n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-b9_4YDQ3eJDy2Fan0gg-5A">Trí Chân thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-N%C4%83ng/Kinh-trung-kh%C3%A1ch-x%C3%A1-v%C4%83n-tranh/poem-wMqWrD4PMZhA17rp2v7mqg">Kinh trung khách xá văn tranh - 京中客舍聞箏</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-N%C4%83ng/author-JKMCauCQ2YDRWsVXXcI4BA">Tiết Năng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%E1%BB%8Bch/M%E1%BB%A5c-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-Y5sh06yqs2uDyT0POQiFng">Mục đồng từ - 牧童詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%E1%BB%8Bch/author-ey1vxXPrGDaptZVsFKS1Uw">Trương Tịch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A3o/Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-k%C3%ADnh/poem-2Do-TgrJnm3vBfpY1RjKLA">Phương kính - 方鏡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A3o/author-zlEhGhvit8FPpDIsa8T0QA">Giả Đảo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BA%A1/T%E1%BA%A9u-m%C3%A3-d%E1%BA%ABn/poem-5CW_ReQgaxfTP_WTDRkhDQ">Tẩu mã dẫn - 走馬引</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BA%A1/author-6YXs2qoM-0pPFaxDDrLTew">Lý Hạ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%A1p-Loa-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Th%E1%BB%8B-t%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-KCJ9ThVP-RQYUlSYcj8C1g">Thị tịch - 示寂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%A1p-Loa-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-FDqhK7bGdfc6Z_aS_7LXLw">Pháp Loa thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Mao-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%C3%B4ng/Thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-ca-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-Du-v%E1%BB%8Bnh/poem-QInvpIy2Eqq-N4XsRLDDTA">Thuỷ điệu ca đầu - Du vịnh - 水調歌頭－遊泳</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Mao-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%C3%B4ng/author-h4yM6-N0eITEQqfS6Lh1ag">Mao Trạch Đông</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
